cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.DS

This paper deals with the detection of location spoofing attacks in the context of IoT, which involves security and networking aspects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the use of statistical decision theory and time-of-arrival information, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and networking (cs.NI), respectively. Additionally, the paper deals with the implementation of the algorithm in existing systems, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
